---
title: Spiced Chicken Breast and Pepper Bulgur with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Yoghurt
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Spiced Chicken Breast and Pepper Bulgur in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220404_R16_W20_UK_QR3538-16_MB_Main_swap_high-a049cad4.jpg
